extends layout

block content
  .container.py-4
    h1.text-center.mb-3 About VortX Database
    p.lead.text-center
      | VortX Database is an application designed to display NBA team and player statistics 
      | using a modern MEAN-style architecture. The project integrates Express, MongoDB, Angular, and 
      | Passport authentication to deliver a smooth and secure user experience.

    hr.my-4

    h3 What Does This Application Do?
    p
      | VortX is an interactive website where users can explore basketball teams, view player 
      | information, and navigate between Western and Eastern Conference teams and statistics. 
    h3 Key Features
    ul
      li User registration and secure login with Passport.js
      li Display of NBA team rosters with Angular components
      li MongoDB database integration for storing user accounts
      li Fully responsive interface built with Bootstrap
      li REST API for retrieving team data
      li Clean, modern UI built using Pug templates and Express routes

    h3 Project Purpose
    p
      | This project was developed as part of a university module on Web Frameworks. It demonstrates an 
      | understanding of MVC architecture, API design, server/client integration, authentication systems, 
      | and modern front-end frameworks.

    h3 Technology Stack
    ul
      li Node.js & Express (server-side)
      li MongoDB & Mongoose (database)
      li Angular (front-end component)
      li Pug templates (HTML rendering)
      li Passport.js (authentication)
      li Bootstrap (responsive UI)

    hr.my-4
